ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The research rotation taught me much about new topics and helped me tuning up my techhniques.

I am starting to learn how to think and design experiments as a scientist. The information I receive everyday is very stimulating. It's exciting to read and figuring out the unanswered question in the field, very challenging at the same time. The process of putting pieces of the puzzle together is hard, but very rewarding.
Helps in the selection of a lab for thesis project.
